Family owned and locally operated since 2006, EDF Pro Inc. provides Montreal and surrounding areas with customized professional home remodeling services. We strive to deliver 100% customer satisfaction through our dedication and expertise to ensure all renovations are completed on schedule, within budget and to our clients expectations. We continuously expand our services through leading edge innovative designs, ideas and techniques all whilst ensuring the highest level of customer satisfaction. 

EDF Pro Inc is a leading home remodeling company specializing in kitchen and bathrooms, room additions, flooring, basement finishing, new deck installation, fencing, insolation, etc. We offer free of charge in-home consultations to help you navigate your way through the maze of twists, turns and details involved in redesigning your home so that your experience is stress free.  One of our experienced team members is available 24/7 to answer any questions you may have or help in an emergency situation.  Please call us at 514-651-8659
